President Trump Announces Supreme Court Nominee: Neil Gorsuch Jan 31, 2017 
President Trump has chosen Neil Gorsuch as his nomination choice for Supreme Court. 
FOX’s Jared Halpern reports from Washington: Five Facts you should know about @POTUS ‘s Supreme Court nominee Judge Neil Gorsuch. Read more: https://t.co/CM01VmfED7 pic.twitter.com/uioZb5GRhk 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 1, 2017 Audio clip:
